flowchart LR
    S[search] -->|always markdown| Q[ingestion queue]
    Q -->|guards: 72h dedup +<br/>must have extracted content| OK[queued]
    OK --> IDLE{{vault idle?<br/>Off / 15 / 30 min}}
    IDLE -->|yes| ING[auto-ingest:<br/>compile + tag entities/concepts<br/>trust-score gate]
    ING --> SETTLE[~60s settle]
    SETTLE --> LINT[auto-lint:<br/>up to 2 passes, prune low value]
    LINT --> CACHE[(continuously maintained,<br/>self-pruning cache)]
